snippet.client:
import (
	context "context"
	customers "github.com/mixed-file-directory/fern/customers"
	fernclient "github.com/mixed-file-directory/fern/client"
	option "github.com/mixed-file-directory/fern/option"
)

client := fernclient.NewClient(
	option.WithToken(
		"<YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN>",
	),
)
response, err := client.Customers.CustomAttributes.Get(
	context.TODO(),
	"customer_id",
	"key",
	&customers.CustomAttributesGetRequest{},
)
